text: Patty Parsons (born in West Virginia) is the former soulful lead singer of AnExchange, a Marin County, California-based folk rock group of the early 1970s. Patty is the aunt of Kat Parsons, a Los Angeles-based singer- songwriter. == External links == * * Patty Parsons *AnExchange * History of AnExchange * Laughing Stock Theatre Company Category:American folk singers Category:AnExchange members Category:Year of birth missing (living people) Category:Living people Category:Singers from West Virginia
